    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example retains its factory-spec Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, providing crisp engagement and direct mechanical feedback. The chassis has been enhanced with reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a refreshed bushing set to maintain optimal suspension geometry under lateral load. The limited-slip M-Variable differential ensures efficient torque transfer, while the braking system remains firm with braided stainless lines. This is a driver-focused machine with a documented service history, including recent valve lash adjustments and a cooling system overhaul. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, its structural and mechanical integrity remains uncompromising.",
      "price": 34500.0,
